    <td valign="top" align="left">
		<font face="verdana" size="2">
		<b>Description:</b> <br>
		This spell will take your hit point and convert it to mana. -8HP------->+8Mana. You should use this if your running low on mana and have a lot of hit points to burn.<BR>
<BR>
<B>Location:</B><BR>General
		</font>
	 </td>
	 <td rowspan="4" valign="top" align="right">
    
